<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,151,775]" pageId="8" pageNumber="49">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,642,667]" pageId="8" pageNumber="49">Remarks.</emphasis>
Hans-Peter Tschorsnig (SMNS) examined the external morphology and sternite 5, cercus, surstylus and the aedeagus of the 
<collectingRegion box="[441,589,678,703]" country="Azerbaijan" name="Naxcivan" pageId="8" pageNumber="49">Nakhichevan</collectingRegion>
