<taxonomicName authorityName=", Tschorsnig" authorityYear="1983" class="Insecta" family="Tachinidae" genus="Bampura" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="49" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angustigena">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="49">B. angustigena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. He also affirmed that the description of the male corresponded with the studied 
<collectingRegion box="[1288,1436,714,739]" country="Azerbaijan" name="Naxcivan" pageId="8" pageNumber="49">Nakhichevan</collectingRegion>
